From 7989e8cb1010b8d151a89ec2dd7d608ff6c40b21 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: CVE Backport <cve@local>
Date: Mon, 25 May 2026 16:24:55 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] fix: Harden parser input handling (CVE-2026-45740 backport to
 v8.0.3)

Backport of upstream 53a27fc4 (#2240) onto protobufjs v8.0.3.

Addresses CVE-2026-45740 (CWE-674: Uncontrolled Recursion) in
Root.fromJSON() and Namespace.addJSON() by introducing util.checkDepth()
and enforcing util.recursionLimit during JSON descriptor parsing and
.proto text parsing.

Co-Authored-By: dcodeIO <dcode@dcode.io>
